When assembling the antenna, don't get too much glue under the antenna board.  I was too liberal with the hot glue; then, the outer antenna enclosure wouldn't fit.  And, in trying to separate the antenna board from the inner enclosure, I managed to damage the board...just another minor setback.<dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://skysedge.com/forum/download/file.php?id=8" class="postimage" alt="20230522_203927.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://skysedge.com/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=128">rwyeth</a> — Tue May 23, 2023 2:02 am</p><hr />
